title: House panel pushes Trump to label Muslim Brotherhood a terror group
description: House Foreign Affairs Committee advances a bipartisan bill urging President Trump to designate the Muslim Brotherhood as a terrorist group.
content:
The House Foreign Affairs Committee advanced legislation Wednesday requiring US President Donald Trump to designate the Muslim Brotherhood as a terrorist organization, JNS reported.
